"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-team-south-africa-bronze-medal-winner-alan-hatherly-its-been-a-dream-since-i-was-a-kid-interview-result-breaking\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9720268865652232, \"rank\": 0.028777759487747297, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbTeam SA medal winner Alan Hatherly: 'It's been a dream since I was a kid'  Long after the crowds had gone home, Alan Hatherly was still trying to come to terms with what he had achieved on Monday afternoon in Paris.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9720268865652232, \"rank\": 0.028777759487747297, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 209, \"end\": 211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8792313487943485e-16, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 225, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Hatherly\", \"score\": 0.9999924602050241, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alan Hatherly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Hatherly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Hatherly\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Hatherly\", \"score\": 0.9999924602050241, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alan Hatherly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Hatherly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Hatherly\"}, {\"begin\": 413, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.3907289216617e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Long after the big crowd had packed up and made their way home,Alan Hatherlywas still trying to come to terms with the enormity of what he had achieved on a muggle Monday afternoon in Paris.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 605, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.3907289216617e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy the Paris Olympic Games 2024 experience at your favourite ATKV Resort!\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ATKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when he wakes up on Monday he will know that the dream is indeed reality.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Team SA cyclist,claimed the Olympicbronzemedal in the men's mountain biking at Paris 2024, becoming the first South African to win a medal in the sport since returning from international isolation at the 1992 Games.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 989, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8792313487943485e-16, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section for free-to-read content  The 28-year-old produced a ride full of character to followTom PidcockandVictor Koretzkyacross the finish in front of where the crowd lined the route in unashamed support of their hometown hero Koretzky.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The eight-lap course at Elancourt Hill offers the most spectacular views of the city and indeed of the iconic Eiffel Tower, but this was no time for sightseeing.\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9lancourt\", \"score\": 0.9999999999663487, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elancourt\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9lancourt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9lancourt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a case of head-down and go through all the pain barriers that would come his way for every second of the 86 minutes and 33 seconds that it would take him to ride his race.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alan Hatherly has always promised big things and arrived in Paris in the form of his life, having won back-to-back World Cup events.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1658, \"end\": 1671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Hatherly\", \"score\": 0.9999924602050241, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alan Hatherly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Hatherly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Hatherly\"}, {\"begin\": 1718, \"end\": 1723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.3907289216617e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his second Olympics he looked to be one of the men to beat.\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And so it proved.\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1871, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was an unbelievable race,\\\" he said a few hours later, still pinching himself.\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was both super fast and tactical.\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I managed to clear the charge early on and led for the first lap.\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The race started to happen after that and I got caught out a bit.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I slipped back (to fifth) and had to chase hard to get back into the medal position.\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And when Tom had his mechanical (puncture) I moved up to second.\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My plan was to empty the tank the last two laps and with Tom coming back I held on to him as he made his way to the front.\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was a massive battle for the medals on that last lap.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's every athlete's dream to get an Olympic medal and now that I have got one, I am still lost for words.\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's going to take some time.\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It still has not sunk in.\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a career goal of mine since I was a child.\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To have achieved it today is such a joy.\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I ticked all the boxes in terms of nothing going wrong and not making mistakes.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's truly a dream come true for me to win a medal for Team SA at the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2862, \"end\": 2864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8792313487943485e-16, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gary Lemkeis reporting live from Paris for the Team SA website for the duration of the Paris Olympics 2024.\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2917, \"end\": 2922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 9.3907289216617e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2936, \"end\": 2938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8792313487943485e-16, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2993, \"end\": 2996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999